### UI and Styling
- Tailwind CSS 3.4.17
- DaisyUI 4.12.24
- Custom UI components
- clsx for class composing
- Heroicons for icon set
- recharts for charts

### State Management
- Redux Toolkit

### Form Handling
- React Hook Form
- Zod for validation

